            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Vel illo atque assumenda consectetur. Nostrum sequi inventore praesentium, id repellat temporibus eos explicabo. Ipsum voluptatibus vel, porro culpa in beatae quis!</p>
            <a href="#About Us" class="btn">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--Brands-->
    <section class="brands" id="brands">
        <div class="heading">
            <span>Brands</span>
            <h3>Our Brands partners</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="brands-container">
            <img src="/img/Google.png" alt="">
